{
  "stem": "7777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They was not used this work what that my friends told me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They was in the woods cutting timbers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was very hard for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Only they live.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They come home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Later, was taking a couple months, the Russian government announced again, all these people what they left, what they don't go to Russia or to Siberia, they have to take passport.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "People were there that was hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They give me a passport with the paragraph 38.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "This mean you had to go away from the border 100 kilometer, about 60 miles, because no good for the country to keep you close to the border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This was in '40, 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I hear there's the town Kostopol not far from [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Zdolbunov ?] on the Russian border, but there was before is we went with some friends where they were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We went over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We live over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And we did little bit again, little bit market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Went to Vilna to Brest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We bought something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "We sold.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "We was turning around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We was over there maybe eight months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Later, I was once Saturday walking in the street, two guys, civil clothes comed over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Come-- come with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They call me to the City Hall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They bring me to City Hall.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "City Hall, they told me, you're doing black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "You will have to go to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Vilicka. ?] Over there is a mine for salt, and you will work over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I come out from the-- when I come out from the City Hall, I start to ask the people what to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vilicka ?] to got to me to work in a mine?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
